        <title>course:smt</title>
        <link>http://flolac.iis.sinica.edu.tw/flolac17/doku.php?id=course:smt&amp;rev=1504514859&amp;do=diff</link>
        <description>Part I

We introduce some first-order theories in this lecture. Some decidable fragments of first-order theories and decision procedures of satisfiability are also introduced. We will learn how to reduce a problem to a problem in satisfiability modulo theories (SMT) and how to use an SMT solver to solve it.</description>
    </item>
